<p><b>Roy Halston Frowick</b> (April 23, 1932 – March 26, 1990), known as <b>Halston</b>, was an American <a href="Fashion_designer" title="Fashion designer" class="mw-redirect">fashion designer</a> of the 1970s. His long dresses or copies of his style were popular fashion wear in mid-1970s <a href="Disco" title="Disco">discotheques</a>.</p>
